---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Templates — AI PM Workbench" description="Reusable templates for AI product management" lang="en">
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3">Templates</h1>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-8 max-w-2xl">Pre-built templates to accelerate your AI product workflow. Use them alongside the Workbench for structured documentation.</p>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="bg-card rounded-xl ring-1 ring-foreground/10 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">AI PM Canvas</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">A 12-dimension framework for structured thinking about AI products. Use before writing PRDs or building prototypes.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">framework</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">12 dimensions</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/AI-PM-Workbench/en/canvas/" class="text-sm text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors">View Canvas &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card rounded-xl ring-1 ring-foreground/10 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Lightweight PRD Template</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">A minimal PRD structure optimized for AI product concepts. Covers problem, user, AI capability, workflow, and evaluation.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">PRD</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">lightweight</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/AI-PM-Workbench/en/ai_prd_lite_template/" class="text-sm text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors">View Template &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card rounded-xl ring-1 ring-foreground/10 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Case Study Template</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">Document your AI product projects as structured case studies. Capture decisions, trade-offs, and lessons learned.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">case study</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">documentation</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/AI-PM-Workbench/en/ai_pm_case_study_template/" class="text-sm text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors">View Template &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-card rounded-xl ring-1 ring-foreground/10 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Workbench Document Pack</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4">Generated by the Workbench: product brief, workflow spec, evaluation plan, acceptance criteria, coding agent handoff, and CLAUDE.md starter.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">generated</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-secondary text-xs text-muted-foreground">6 documents</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/AI-PM-Workbench/en/workbench/" class="text-sm text-emerald-400 hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors">Open Workbench &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
